  "question": "We propose to calculate a $95 \\%$ confidence interval for the risk difference in the estrogen trial presented earlier. We've established that $a_1=751$ and $n_1=8506$ in the treatment group. In the control group, $a_2=623$ and $n_2=8102$.",
